intro: Shoot the bubbles and match 3 of the same color. A beautiful classic with kitties!
description:
-Classic bubble-shooter mechanics with smooth, precise controls
-99 carefully designed levels with varied goals and layouts
-Distinct kitty characters that add charm and personality to each stage
-Colorful, appealing graphics and gentle sound design
-Special bubble types, boosters, and power-ups for more advanced puzzles
-A blend of objective-based and traditional bubble-clearing levels
